internal/tifflzw/ contains an LZW reader/writer adapted from:
  - golang.org/x/image/tiff/lzw (reader; the upstream "off by one" comment is preserved)
  - the Go standard library compress/lzw (writer; the same off-by-one
    transition is applied symmetrically so the writer's output is decodable
    by libtiff, imagecodecs, and golang.org/x/image/tiff/lzw)

